MUSAEO Dris. BOISDUVAL; 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Boisduval" authorityYear="1869" box="[1115,1358,1027,1051]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Argynnis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mormonia">Argynnis Mormonia</taxonomicName>
[male] Bdv. ex typ. sp.; Oberthur Collection; Barnes Collection”
